      <div class="page-header-area">
        <h1 class="page-title">Sidebar Navigation Level 1</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">A vertical icon-based sidebar navigation panel used across all UEMS product modules. Supports two display modes &#8212; expanded (icon + label) and collapsed (icon only) &#8212; with up to 8 configurable item slots and a fixed bottom action row.</p>
