          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h3 id="content-guidelines" class="doc-h3">Content Guidelines<span class="h3-badge" style="background:rgba(37,99,235,0.1);color:var(--prism-violet);">Recommended</span></h3>
            <div class="do-dont-grid">
              <div class="do-card"><span class="card-label">Do</span><ul>
                <li>Always set exactly one item to <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Active</code> to reflect the current page.</li>
                <li>Use the <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Add</code> state only for primary creation actions (e.g. "Add Config").</li>
                <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> only as the collapsed state, toggled by the user.</li>
                <li>Show tooltips on all items when in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> mode.</li>
                <li>Keep all items from the product's defined set &#8212; disable rather than hide items users shouldn't access.</li>
              </ul></div>
              <div class="dont-card"><span class="card-label">Don't</span><ul>
                <li>Leave all items in <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Default</code> &#8212; users need a clear location indicator.</li>
                <li>Use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Add</code> state for regular navigation destinations.</li>
                <li>Default to <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> &#8212; expanded labels aid discoverability.</li>
                <li>Hide labels in collapsed mode without providing a hover tooltip.</li>
                <li>Remove items from the nav list for items that are merely restricted &#8212; use <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Disabled</code> state with a tooltip explaining why.</li>
              </ul></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== STYLE ========== -->
        <div class="tab-content" id="tab-style" style="display:none;padding-top:32px;">
          <h2 id="style-overview" class="doc-section-title">Style</h2>
          <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens, size specifications, and visual states that define the Sidebar Navigation Level 1 appearance.</p>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="variants" class="doc-section-title">Variants</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Each product component set exposes one variant axis.</p>
            <table class="size-table">
              <thead><tr><th>Axis</th><th>Values</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr><td><strong>Type</strong></td><td><code>Icon with Text</code>, <code>Icon Only</code></td><td>Expanded (72px wide, icon + label) vs. collapsed (44px wide, icon only).</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <hr class="doc-divider"/>

          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="item-states" class="doc-section-title">Item States</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Each nav item supports five interaction states controlling background, icon color, and label color.</p>
            <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(130px,1fr));gap:14px;margin-top:24px;">
              <div style="padding:24px 16px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--prism-surface);border:1px solid var(--prism-border);text-align:center;">
                <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
                  <div class="sidebar-nav-demo" style="width:auto;height:auto;border:none;background:none;padding:0;">
                    <button class="nav-item-demo" style="pointer-events:none;">
                      <span class="nav-item-demo__icon-wrap"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="24" height="24"><path d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-4 0a1 1 0 01-1-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 01-1 1"/></svg></span>
                      <span class="nav-item-demo__label">Item</span>
