          <div class="doc-section">
            <h2 id="references" class="doc-section-title">References</h2>
            <p class="doc-section-subtitle">Design tokens and resources for implementing the Sidebar Navigation Level 1 component.</p>
            <ul class="doc-list">
              <li><strong>Figma Node:</strong> <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">16780:88270</code> &#8212; Component Set: Left Navigation Level 1</li>
              <li><strong>Product Sets:</strong> 15 pre-configured component sets, one per UEMS product module</li>
              <li><strong>Sub-component:</strong> Left Nav Item L1 (<code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">_base_Left Nav Item L1</code>)</li>
              <li><strong>Variant Axis:</strong> Type &#8212; <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon with Text</code> (72px) / <code style="font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:6px;background:rgba(37,99,235,0.06);color:var(--prism-violet);">Icon Only</code> (44px)</li>
